/* International designation of Hamas */ For all intents and purposes, Canada considers a "group or individual associated with terrorism" to be a "terrorist" or "terrorist entity." Osama bin Laden's "association with terrorism" made him a terrorist.

Canada OFFICIALLY classifies Hamas as a terrorist "entity" (essentially an organization) ALONGSIDE the likes of Al Qaida and Hezbollah. Canadian law provides no distinction between listed terrorist groups and groups "associated with terrorism."
Added Canada to the list of countries that consider Hamas a terrorist organization

/* Usage */ Canadian ovens can't be "configured" to show either Fahrenheit or Celsius. In fact, most "Canadian" ovens are made using specifications unique to the entire North American market. The source provided also makes note of this.

Removed "rarely" pertaining to Canadian use of the mile. Rarely used or not, the mile is still used in Canada (railways, horse racing, etc). Full stop.
